strings: <voice_0x01000B3F><se_def>*: Wait a second, who is there?
<voice_0x01000B40><se_def>*: I don't know how I'm doing. What are you doing here
<voice_0x01000B41><se_def>*: A special permit is required to come here.
<voice_0x01000B42><se_def>*: tell jokes! If you don't want to die fighting a Templar Swordsman today!
<voice_0x01000B43><se_def>*: Please keep strangers away so as not to appear arrogant. We have a nice name, but would you be ashamed of the Templars?
<voice_0x01000B45><se_def>Awesome!: I apologize for the violence of my people. I've come across a strange problem. not very tall
<voice_0x01000B46><se_def>Awesome!: Our task is the protection of mathematics. We cannot allow foreigners to move about freely.
<voice_0x01000B47><se_def>Awesome!: Maths are tough, but you don't care!
<voice_0x01000B48><se_def>Awesome!: After all, this is the home of the Templars. There doesn't seem to be much to do here so I'd like you to leave.
<voice_0x01000B49><se_def>Awesome!: Tell us that our employees are worried that next time we won't be able to stop them.
<voice_0x01000B4A><se_def>*: what time is it now? what time is it do you have an angel ring
<voice_0x01000B4B><se_def>*: Good morning, Do you think you still owe? How sad this kid is!
<voice_0x01000B4D><se_def>*: I never thought about it! The angel is here, hurry up!
